 class="md-image-responsive" />
&lt;/div>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Validate and Deploy Resources</title><link>https://cloud.layer5.io/academy/learning-paths/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111/mastering-kubernetes-for-engineers/deploying-wordpress-and-mysql-with-persistent-volumes-with-meshery/sql/deploy/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://cloud.layer5.io/academy/learning-paths/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111/mastering-kubernetes-for-engineers/deploying-wordpress-and-mysql-with-persistent-volumes-with-meshery/sql/deploy/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="deploy-the-resources" class="heading-link">
